input: A bustling city street at night.\nNeon lights illuminate the scene.
output: A crowded city street teeming with life under a blanket of velvet night skies. Towering buildings boast vibrant neon signs, casting an otherworldly glow on hurrying pedestrians and gleaming vehicles. Streetlamps cast a warm, amber light, illuminating rain-slicked asphalt reflecting the colorful chaos above. A sense of exhilaration and endless possibility should permeate the image.
